[2] Illinois (Cook County)
Date: Mon 2 Dec 2019 1:05 PM CST
Source: CBS [abridged, edited]
https://chicago.cbslocal.com/2019/12/02/oak-park-river-forest-high-school-reports-another-case-of-whooping-cough/


A 3rd student at Oak Park River Forest [OPRF] High School has been diagnosed with whooping cough, school officials said. Workers are "diligently performing extra sweeps to clean and sanitize the building," OPRF said in a statement. A 4th case involving an adult was also reported.

